data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom villa located in  the 55+ community of Delray Villas. The property features a large living area, dining room, ample bedrooms, Florida room, a one car garage, and no rear neighbors. The low HOA fees include cable, lawn maintenance, and common area maintenance. This is the perfect location with shopping, dining, beaches, and all the fun South Florida has to offer just minutes away.
